    "description": "Metropolis Healthcare Asia Pacific Associates has an exciting opening for a Surgeon at our Srinagar office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Metropolis Healthcare Asia Pacific Associates:\nMetropolis Healthcare Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in ICU Management\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Flexible working hours\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Metropolis Healthcare Asia Pacific Associates!",
